magic.title: Magic Items
description: ## main/magic_armor View Magic Armor and Shields

## main/magic_misc View Miscellaneous Magic Items || Includes: Altars, Construct Modifications, Elemental Augmentations, Favors, Fetishes, Fleshcrafting, Fungal grafts, Implants, Infused poisons, Necrografts, Necrotoxins, Oils, Plants, Relics, Piercings, Talismans, Tattoos, Thrones, and Magical Sets.

magic_enhancements.title: Magic - Enhancements
description: Adding an enhancement to armor, shields, and weapons raises the base price of the [armor, shield](rule/magic_armor), or [weapon](rule/magic_weapons) being enhanced. This is either equivalent to a standard +1 (or other) bonus, or it's a fixed amount of gold.
